Class BounceAuthServlet

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, javax.servlet.Servlet, javax.servlet.ServletConfig

    public class BounceAuthServlet
extends SessionServlet
    An implementation of the IdP end of the remote authentication protocol used by RemoteAuthServlet. This is if we wish to implement this protocol between two safe versions. Parameters are:
    • remote_auth_servlet.url url of RemoteAuthServlet
    • remote_auth_servlet.realm realm to generate name from.
    • remote_auth_servlet.secret Secret to use in auth
    • remote_auth_servlet.hash Hash algorithm to use
    Author:
    spb
